Description
===========
Writes fields about the mesh-quality to disk for visualization

"Original" Author
=================
Bernhard Gschaider (bgschaid@ice-sf.at)

Current Maintainer
==================
Bernhard Gschaider (bgschaid@ice-sf.at)

Documentation
=============
Writes volScalarFields to disk:
	nonOrtohgonal: 	nonortogonality of the cells
	skewness:	skewness of the cells
	cellVolume:	volume of the cells
	wallDist:	distance of the boundary-patch-faces to the cell-centers


Required OpenFOAM-Version (Known to work with)
==============================================
1.4.1 
(propably works for older versions, but not tested)

Directory Contents
==================
meshQualityFields: source code of the utility
